pasturage licence
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an early legal agreement by which runholders could acquire land for grazing.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
